      • KEY_PRTSCR

        static final int KEY_PRTSCR
        PrtScr key. Note: for use on keyboards with a PrtScr key that is separate from the SysRq key. Most keyboards combine SysRq and PrtScr so if the intent is to actually capture the user's desire to capture the screen then SysRq is the most likely scan code. Use PrtScr to catch the rest (laptops, mini-keyboards, etc.)
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
